            "fi-fi": {
              "display_title": "TOXIC REAPA",
              "description": "”Sankarit! TOXIC REAPA on paennut Hero Factorysta, se on nähty matkallaan kotiplaneetalleen Z’chayaan. Se on saatava kiinni, mutta olkaa varovaisia. Sillä on aseenaan kuolettavaa myrkkyä, musertavat kourat ja tehokas laserleikkuri. Sankarit, luotamme teihin!”",
              "title": "TOXIC REAPA",
              "tags": []
            },
            "en-us": {
              "bullet_points": "•  Features toxic tanks, toxic jets, crushing claws and laser cutters\r\n•  Highly flexible and poseable elements\r\n•  Includes unique code for 200 game points for LEGO Hero Factory BREAKOUT game\r\n•  Battle with hero 6200 EVO!\r\n•  Combine with 6200 EVO for an even bigger model!\r\n•  Stands over 6” (15cm) tall!",
              "display_title": "TOXIC REAPA",
              "description": "“Heroes! TOXIC REAPA has escaped from Hero Factory and has been detected on his to home planet of Z’chaya. We need you to recapture him quick, but use caution. He’s armed with a deadly toxic waste attack, crushing claws and powerful laser cutters. Heroes, we’re counting on you!”",
